self.sensors = Sensors()
self.sensors.add(name='SenseTmpDirState', shell=
    'if [ -d "/tmp/goap_tmp" ]; then echo -n "exist"; else echo -n "not_exist"; fi'
    , binding='tmp_dir_state')
self.sensors.add(name='SenseTmpDirContent', shell=
    '[ -f /tmp/goap_tmp/.token ] && echo -n "token_found" || echo -n "token_not_found"'
    , binding='tmp_dir_content')
assert 'SenseTmpDirState' == str(self.sensors.get(name='SenseTmpDirState'))
assert 'SenseTmpDirContent' == str(self.sensors.get(name='SenseTmpDirContent'))
